trans-unit.source: Represents an element in a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection" /> class.
The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class represents the \<schemeSettings> element under the Uri section within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> 클래스는 \<schemeSettings > 구성 파일 내에서 Uri 섹션 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> class represents an instance of an element in the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> 클래스에 있는 요소의 인스턴스를 나타내며는 <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class and the \<schemeSettings> section in a configuration file looks generic, implying that an application can specify any <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for any scheme.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> 클래스 및 \<schemeSettings > 구성 파일의 섹션 의미 하는 제네릭 응용 프로그램 하나를 지정할 수 <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> 모든 체계에 대 한 열거형 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: In fact, only the <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions.DontUnescapePathDotsAndSlashes?displayProperty=nameWithType> flag for HTTP and HTTPS schemes are supported.
trans-unit.target: 실제로는 <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions.DontUnescapePathDotsAndSlashes?displayProperty=nameWithType> HTTP 및 HTTPS 스키마는 지원 되는 플래그를 지정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> class.
Gets the value of the GenericUriParserOptions entry from a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> instance.

The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> property returns a <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instance.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> 속성에서 반환 된 <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> 열거형 값에 대 한는 <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> 인스턴스.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the Name entry from a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> instance.
The protocol used by this schema setting.

The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> property returns a <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instance.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> 속성에서 반환 된 <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> 열거형 값에 대 한는 <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> 인스턴스.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> element is currently restricted to HTPP and HTTPS.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> 요소는 현재 HTPP 및 HTTPS를 제한 합니다.
